<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-pickle-pink via-pickle-yellow to-pickle-teal opacity-95"></div>
  <div class="absolute -left-24 -top-28 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-white/20 blur-2xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-black/10 blur-2xl"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-10 md:grid-cols-12 md:items-center md:py-14">
    <div class="md:col-span-7">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/15 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-white/95 ring-1 ring-white/25">
        <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-white"></span>
        匹克球比賽申請表
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-[Montserrat] text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white md:text-4xl">
        <%= tournament.name %>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-2xl text-white/90">
        填寫個人資料並選擇年齡組別提交報名。提交後我們會以電郵確認。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/90">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/15 px-3 py-2 ring-1 ring-white/20">
          <span class="font-semibold">日期</span>：<%= tournament.date %>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/15 px-3 py-2 ring-1 ring-white/20">
          <span class="font-semibold">地點</span>：<%= tournament.location %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-5">
      <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-xl">
        <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white/10 ring-1 ring-white/20 backdrop-blur">
          <img
            src="/images/tournament-poster.png"
            alt="比賽海報"
            class="h-auto w-full object-contain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

